# Debug reports

- Full payload stored in DB/admin (`/admin/debug-reports/{public_id}`).
- Telegram: opt-in, short summary + admin link only — never full JSON.
- Sanitize: Authorization, Cookie, tokens, secrets, passwords, API keys, env values.
- Coordinates coarse/rounded by default (`allow_precise_coordinates` to opt in).
- Telegram failure must not fail report creation.
- Public: `POST /debug-reports`; `?debug=1` enables copy/send diagnostics.

## Env (no secrets in repo)

`CITYGO_DEBUG_REPORTS_TELEGRAM_ENABLED` · `CITYGO_DEBUG_REPORTS_TELEGRAM_CHAT_ID` · `CITYGO_DEBUG_REPORTS_ADMIN_BASE_URL`
